WEBVTT

00:00.720 --> 00:01.560
Report to Your Highness

00:01.880 --> 00:02.600
I never expected

00:02.840 --> 00:04.440
Huaicheng's commander Lu Yuan

00:04.880 --> 00:06.400
Was once Yugong's student

00:06.800 --> 00:07.400
I

00:07.520 --> 00:08.920
Originally wanted to persuade him to surrender

00:09.000 --> 00:10.480
But he cursed Your Highness

00:10.480 --> 00:12.040
As unrighteous and unjust

00:13.680 --> 00:15.200
I had no choice but to attack

00:15.240 --> 00:16.240
And beheaded him

00:16.440 --> 00:17.240
This battle

00:18.160 --> 00:19.600
Our army suffered heavy losses

00:22.720 --> 00:23.440
Your Highness

00:23.600 --> 00:24.400
Don't look anymore

00:31.280 --> 00:32.200
Back then

00:32.720 --> 00:34.240
I wronged him
